The lack of information on the candidate's proficiency in AngularJS, specifically mentioned in the job description, further lowers the potential match percentage. If the resume demonstrates proficiency in most of the 'need to have' skills and some of the 'nice to have' skills, along with the relevant experience, the match percentage could be significantly higher.
